claim.claim-text:
A wireless charging apparatus 100 comprising:
a charging resonance unit 120 for wireless charging;
a driving circuit unit 110 to which the charging resonance unit 120 is connected and to which an internal circuitry is mounted;
a shield member 130 mounted to a rear surface of the charging resonance unit 120; and
a heat dispersion member 140 mounted to the driving circuit unit 110 and the shield member 130 to disperse heat generated by the driving circuit unit 110.
